1395
00:51:11,040 --> 00:51:14,820
The partition function is the sum over all configurations.

1396
00:51:17,259 --> 00:51:21,020
That means it's the sum over n and m

1397
00:51:21,880 --> 00:51:23,850
such that little n plus little

1398
00:51:23,850 --> 00:51:25,820
m is equal to big N.

1399
00:51:25,900 --> 00:51:26,900
I won't bother writing that,

1400
00:51:26,900 --> 00:51:28,100
but keep that in mind.

1401
00:51:28,620 --> 00:51:33,720
Times e to the minus beta times the energy,

1402
00:51:33,720 --> 00:51:40,240
which is mu h times n minus m.

1403
00:51:43,680 --> 00:51:45,280
So we just take this thing

1404
00:51:45,280 --> 00:51:46,880
and we add them all up.

1405
00:51:48,720 --> 00:51:49,360
Now,

1406
00:51:49,360 --> 00:51:51,520
for each n minus m,

1407
00:51:51,840 --> 00:51:54,500
there's going to be a certain number of configurations,

1408
00:51:54,640 --> 00:51:56,740
and that number of configurations

1409
00:51:56,740 --> 00:51:58,840
is this combinatoric coefficient here.

1410
00:51:59,220 --> 00:52:01,300
So we can write this...

1411
00:52:01,300 --> 00:52:01,980
Yeah.

1412
00:52:04,700 --> 00:52:05,100
n,

1413
00:52:05,100 --> 00:52:07,100
nm is not too variable.

1414
00:52:09,460 --> 00:52:09,860
Yeah,

1415
00:52:09,860 --> 00:52:10,220
they are.

1416
00:52:10,320 --> 00:52:11,900
The number of ups and the number of downs.

1417
00:52:12,460 --> 00:52:12,860
Well,

1418
00:52:12,860 --> 00:52:14,530
I'm just saying it's not two

1419
00:52:14,530 --> 00:52:16,200
