1420
00:52:17,320 --> 00:52:18,820
They have to add up to capital N.

1421
00:52:18,820 --> 00:52:19,140
That's all.

1422
00:52:20,020 --> 00:52:20,420
So,

1423
00:52:20,420 --> 00:52:22,380
but I'm just saying if you have...

1424
